query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b1) */ select b1.name,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('sharepoint',
'wordpress') AND t1.name IN ('categories',
'custom-taxonomy',
'document-library',
'hooks',
'images',
'javascript',
'navigation',
'pages',
'permalinks',
'sharepoint-online',
'themes',
'widgets',
'wpdb')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%com'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id group by b1.name order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
